                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="mb-3 h-8 w-8 text-gray-400 peer-checked:text-emerald-600 dark:text-gray-500 dark:peer-checked:text-emerald-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
